releaseNotes: - New Debug interface for reading the debug log and running debug commands.
- Scene selection inplemented. Teases can define which Scenes are eligible to start from and the Title Card of those Scenes.
- Button to open the Engine Settings folder added to debug tab.
- Qml cache on Windows is in the same Folder as the settings since Windows doesn't have a dedicated cache folder.
- Scene Resources update if the resource is removed or changed somewhere else.
- Fixed some constellations of Scene transitions that failed to transition correctly.

- Fixed a race condition when executing scripts. The new implementation is completely decoupled from the UI. Even if the UI elements are deleted while executing the scripts, the script will continue to execute though the commands will do nothing.
